data.description: Immaculate full brick home with NO HOA! This 4 bed 2.5 bath home offers the epitome of comfortable living. Large formal living and dining rooms are perfect for entertaining while the separate family room invites you to relax and unwind by the cozy fireplace. The spacious dine-in kitchen stands at the heart of the home offering a breakfast bar and plenty of cabinet and counter space for ample storage. New homeowners will love the peaceful primary suite while the 3 additional bedrooms share a full hall bath ensuring privacy and comfort for family and guests. Outside, the backyard includes a patio, storage building, and 3 gates to accommodate, boats, trailers, and other outdoor equipment. Located just minutes from I-95 & centrally located between Fort Stewart and Savannah, this home is a MUST see!
